4.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Like-A-Dragon-The-Man-Who-Erased-His-Name-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Like-A-Dragon-The-Man-Who-Erased-His-Name-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Like-A-Dragon-The-Man-Who-Erased-His-Name-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Like-A-Dragon-The-Man-Who-Erased-His-Name-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3545298" class="wp-caption-text">像龙一样：抹去名字的男人（提供：Ryu Ga Gotoku Studio）</figcaption></figure><p>目前尚不清楚<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/like-a-dragon-gaiden-the-man-who-erased-his-name">《如龙：抹去名字的人》</a></em>和<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/call-of-duty-modern-warfare-3">《使命召唤：现代战争 3》等</a></em>较新的游戏是否会包含在此次销售中，因为之前的销售要么完全排除了较新的游戏，要么只包含了最新的游戏。与其他游戏相比，他们给予了小幅折扣。</p><p>近日，《<em>如龙：抹去名字的男人》</em>团队<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/like-a-dragon-gaiden-the-man-who-erased-his-name-interview-karaoke-christmas-song-3540128">与《NME》讨论了卡拉OK的吸引力</a><em><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/like-a-dragon-gaiden-the-man-who-erased-his-name-interview-karaoke-christmas-song-3540128">，</a></em>并解释了他们如何通过新作品迎接圣诞节。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/heres-when-the-steam-black-friday-sale-kicks-off-3545257">这篇文章《Steam 黑色星期五特卖即将开始》</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
