473207">粉丝重制了整个游戏</a>，但它永远不会发行。</p><p>在其他游戏新闻中，滚石乐队已确认与<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/ea-sports-fc-24"><em>EA Sports FC 24</em></a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/the-rolling-stones-confirm-ea-sports-fc-24-collaboration-3544458">合作</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/the-simpsons-hit-run-developer-talks-bizarre-decision-to-scrap-sequel-3545309">《辛普森一家肇事逃亡》开发商谈论取消续集的“奇怪决定”的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
